# Feature to Requirements Mapping — Student Productivity App

---

## Feature: User Authentication

**Functional Requirements:**
- Students must be able to register using a valid email address and password
- Students must be able to log in and log out of their accounts
- The system must support password reset via email verification
- Passwords must be validated for minimum length and complexity

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- Login response must complete within 2 seconds under normal load
- All passwords must be stored using secure hashing (e.g., bcrypt)
- The system must use HTTPS to encrypt all data in transit
- The session must expire after 30 minutes of inactivity for security

---

## Feature: Class Schedule Management

**Functional Requirements:**
- Students must be able to add a class with fields: subject name, day, start time, end time, and location
- Students must be able to view their schedule in a weekly calendar layout
- Students must be able to edit or delete any class entry they have created
- The system must prevent scheduling conflicts (overlapping times on the same day)

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- The schedule view must load within 2 seconds
- The calendar must display correctly on both mobile and desktop screen sizes
- Data must be saved persistently so the schedule is available on next login

---

## Feature: Assignment Tracking

**Functional Requirements:**
- Students must be able to create an assignment with a title, subject, due date, and description
- Students must be able to update assignment status: To Do, In Progress, or Done
- Students must be able to set a priority level: High, Medium, or Low
- Students must be able to delete assignments they no longer need
- Assignments must be sortable and filterable by due date, subject, or status

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- Assignment list must load within 2 seconds even with 100+ entries
- Changes to assignment status must be saved immediately without page refresh
- The system must support at least 500 concurrent student users without performance degradation

---

## Feature: Study Session Planner

**Functional Requirements:**
- Students must be able to create a study session with subject, date, start time, and end time
- Students must be able to view all planned sessions in a calendar view
- Students must be able to edit or delete study sessions
- The system must display total planned study hours per subject per week

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- Study session calendar must load within 2 seconds
- The planner must work offline and sync when the device reconnects to the internet
- Session data must not be lost if the app is closed unexpectedly

---

## Feature: Notifications and Reminders

**Functional Requirements:**
- The system must send push notifications for assignment deadlines based on user-defined lead time (1, 2, or 3 days before)
- The system must send class reminders a configurable number of minutes before each class
- Students must be able to enable or disable individual notification types in settings
- The system must deliver a daily morning summary of the day's classes and deadlines

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- Notifications must be delivered within 60 seconds of the scheduled trigger time
- Notification delivery must achieve 99% reliability
- The system must not send duplicate notifications for the same event

---

## Feature: Dashboard Overview

**Functional Requirements:**
- The dashboard must display today's classes, assignments due within 7 days, and pending tasks
- The dashboard must show a progress bar per subject indicating task completion percentage
- The dashboard must be personalised to the logged-in student's data only

**Non-Functional Requirements:**
- Dashboard must load within 3 seconds after login
- Dashboard data must reflect real-time changes made elsewhere in the app without manual refresh
- The UI must be accessible and readable on screens as small as 360px wide (mobile-first design)
